reviewText: These workouts are all pretty much the same, short in length, low impact, and the same moves in all of dvds. I bought many of the other dvds to have a variety of ideas to use for the bender ball but haven't gotten too many.

This is just another poorly directed, money-making production for the Bender producers. The workout is a waste of time. If you're looking for something that is worth your time, and your money, look elsewhere. It is not here.
